Introduction

H&D (Korean: 에이치앤디; Japanese: エイチアンディ) is a duo consisting of Lee Hangyul and Nam Dohyon, both well known for being former members of the group X1 and current members of the group BAE173. They made their official debut in February 2020 with the song called "Toward Tomorrow".

The duo is presumably disbanded with the departure of Dohyon from BAE173 and the company.
